5
) Median furrow of propodeum not delimited by submedian ridges (

Fig. 
25

); 
6
) notauli obliterated by the sculpture of the mesoscutum (

Fig. 
22

); 
7
) axillar grooves obliterated anteriorly (

Fig. 
22

); 
8
) pedicel short, with bottle-neck base (Fig. 
14
